Now we will bind the input controller with the weight and height field. It will help us in getting the value from the field.
final TextEditingController _heightController = TextEditingController();
  final TextEditingController _weightController = TextEditingController();

Now we have defined two controller for two Text Field. Let attach to the the respective text field, So that we could have control over the Text Field.
TextField(
  controller: _heightController,  // Added
  decoration: InputDecoration(
    labelText: 'height in cm',
    icon: Icon(Icons.trending_up),
  ),
),
